data.description: Welcome to your charming bungalow, freshly rehabbed in 2022! New roof, windows, HVAC, flooring, and stainless steel appliances grace this cozy home. The kitchen boasts new cabinets, granite countertops, and a gas stove. A utility room, large backyard with two sheds, and easy access to the interstate make this an ideal starter home or investment property. Schedule a showing today!
